Some drawbacks...
Limited to about 100 miles per tank of air...
Limited top speed and acceleration...
Takes about four hours to refill the tank
with the car's built-in compressor...
Although the car itself is clean 'n green,
the electricity to run the compressor
might not be...A coal fired electric gen-
erator might be the source of the car's
electric compressor...

